</code></pre> You can these functions to change loading screen texts in runtime, or you can opt to ignore those functions.</p> <p>For example create a class BiometricFaceCaptureLoadingCustomView, create a layout file and bind it.</p> <pre><code>class CustomFaceCaptureLoadingView @JvmOverloads constructor(
    context: Context,
